-Insect Order Mantodea (Mantises);
-Insect Order Odonata (Dragonflies and Damselflies);
-Insect Order Megaloptera (Alderflies, Dobsonflies, and Fishflies);
-Insect Order Neuroptera (Antlions, Lacewings, and Allies);
-Insect Family Coccinellidae (Lady Beetles);
-Class Chilopoda (Centipedes);
-Class Arachnida (Arachnids)
